@startuml
title Dedup by Consumer\nFix: commit consumer offset in my SQL
hide footbox
participant KBroker
database SQL order 10

=== Offsets stored in Broker (classic) ====
KBroker<-KConsumer: poll(batch: 50)
KConsumer->KConsumer: 50 x process(M)
KBroker<-KConsumer: Ack(offset: 50)
hnote over KBroker: offset=50

=== Offsets stored in SQL ====

KBroker<-KConsumer: poll(50 from offset 7)
KConsumer++

KBroker-->KConsumer: M1\noffset:7
hnote over KConsumer: processing
group transaction
KConsumer->SQL: update(s)
KConsumer->SQL: update next_offset=8
end
hnote over SQL: offset=8
KConsumer--
KBroker<-KConsumer: poll from offset 8
KConsumer++
KBroker->KConsumer: M2\noffset:8
@enduml